     <div type="encomium">
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <l>BRaue <hi>LOGIE,</hi> so continue to beate downe,</l>
   <l>By Scripture, Fathers, Reason, what is hatched</l>
   <l>Against the Trueth, by Doctors of new <hi>Rome:</hi>
   </l>
   <l>And show, that much of Vntrueths is but patched,</l>
   <l>Which they maintaine. So Trueth shall Thee vp-holde,</l>
   <l>And make Thy foes to quaile, but Thee more bolde.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Amoris ergo posuit Cargillus.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
